Install meta-mask from here: https://metamask.io/

For Linux
Commands for installing nodejs and Ganache-cli: 
1.curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_8.x | sudo -E bash -
2.sudo apt-get install -y nodejs
3.npm install -g ganache-cli


For Windows
	Ganache-gui is also available. For windows we can download ganache-gui(desktop application).
Download ganache-gui  from here: https://github.com/trufflesuite/ganache/releases.
